n the\nnon-zero spectrum of L_X on odd forms. We also can deform with D_X' = [B_X,D_X]\nof D_X=d+i_X + b_X, B_X=d_X-d_X^*+i b_X the exterior derivative d governed by\nthe vector field X.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Nov 2018 00:27:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-27"}
