tation: A subject-specific breast model allows a better\ncharacterization of breast mechanics. However, the model presents some\nlimitations when estimating the supine tilted breast configuration. The results\nshow clearly the difficulties to characterize soft tissues mechanics at large\nstrain ranges with Neo-Hookean material models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Nov 2018 07:54:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-27"}
