e involved stochastic processes combine\nand, from an applicative point of view, by the construction of confidence\nintervals for the common limit inclination of the agents and of a test\nstatistics to make inference on the matrix $W$, based on the weighted empirical\nmeans. In particular, we answer a research question posed in [arXiv:1705.02126,\nBernoulli, Forth.]\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Nov 2018 09:53:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-10"}
