th length were fixed to its $75^{th}$ percentile value, the\nharmful effect of the metal mixture on neurodevelopment is attenuated,\nsuggesting nutritional interventions to help increase fetal growth, and thus\nbirth length, could potentially block the harmful effect of the metal mixture\non neurodevelopment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Nov 2018 15:32:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 16 Aug 2019 09:13:35 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 21 Dec 2021 20:57:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-23"}
